nroffed_file ({0,2,14,"%^BOLD%^new shop owner","Discworld shop help","new shop owner%^RESET%^","",8,"Black listing people",3,5,5,"You can deny people complete access to your shop if you, so they have no ability to either buy or sell items.  To do this you use the black list control in the shop.  Black listing is checked before everything else and overrides everything.To add someone to your black list go 'approve black list add <person>' and to remove someone from your black list go 'approve black list remove <person>'.  You can also add all the people from your ignore list to the black list if you wish by going 'approve black list add ignore'.You can see the current people in your black list using the 'approve status' command. ","",8,"Examples",7,5,"> approve black list add brighidYou add brighid to the black list.> approve statusPeople allowed to change the shop are lanfear.People denied access to the shop are brighidThe current percentage to automatically add to the buy price is: 20%Automatically approve sales less than       : 50p.Automatically accept sales by               : none.Automatically accept sales to the categories:     Sex Aids             max value A$100     Healing Aids         max value A$3Automatically accept sales of               :     business card        max value A$3Limits on what can be sold.Maximum number of items allowed in the shop : 100.Maximum number of items allowed per player  : 20.Automatically queue sales more than         : A$100.Automatically deny sales more than          : disabled.Limits set per player.   Name            Max Sellable    Approve Limit        Deny limit (per item)   pinkfish        10              A$10                 A$10   brighid         25              A$5                  A$20Current money spent A$262.15 and money made A$118.49.> approve black list remove brighidYou remove brighid from the black list.> appove black list add ignoreYou add brighid, lanfear and yukk to the black list.","",})
